{"type":"message","id":"93e8e970","parentId":"08c1a297","timestamp":"2026-04-29T07:02:57.990Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-04-29 03:00 EDT] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Reflections: Theme: `18-21` kept surfacing across 68 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:33-36, memory/2026-04-10.md:37-40, memory/2026-04-10.md:41-44; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `26-29` kept surfacing across 68 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:37-40, memory/2026-04-10.md:41-44, memory/2026-04-10.md:45-48; note: reflection\n- Possible Lasting Truths: Possible Lasting Truths: No strong candidate truths surfaced. [confidence=0.58 evidence=memory/2026-04-10.md:12-12]; Reflections: Theme: `1.00` kept surfacing across 16 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:18-21, memory/2026-04-10.m\n- Reflections: Theme: `kept` kept surfacing across 79 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:26-29, memory/2026-04-10.md:30-33, memory/2026-04-10.md:34-37; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `memory/2026-04-10.md` kept surfacing across 104 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:18-21, memory/2026-04-10.md:22-25, memory/2026-04-10.md:26-29; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `reflections` kept surfacing across 104 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:9-9, memory/2026-04-10.md:18-18, memory/2026-04-10.md:18-21; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `18-21` kept surfacing across 37 memories.; confidence: 0.97; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:33-36, memory/2026-04-10.md:37-40, memory/2026-04-10.md:41-44; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `theme` kept surfacing across 102 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:18-21, memory/2026-04-10.md:22-25, memory/2026-04-10.md:26-29; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `1.00` kept surfacing across 95 memories.; confidence: 1.00; e